{"tid":2429691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳言新版「超人」將有望由非裔演員擔任","createTime":"2021-03-02T13:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T14:50:38.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ead668ef187c4fdde31b4999b19f180467150458","tid":2429691,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"傳言新版「超人」將有望由非裔演員擔任<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2021/2/superman-reboot-black-ta-nehisi-coates-warner-bros-info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2021%2F2%2Fsuperman-reboot-black-ta-nehisi-coates-warner-bros-info&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=5edef1b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2021/2/superman-reboot-black-ta-nehisi-coates-warner-bros-info</a><br />\n<br />\n根據 Hollywood Reporter 報導證實，DC 旗下《超人》系列有望推出全新版本，製作方改由 J. J. Abrams 主導的製片公司 Bad Robot 負責，而新的超人將有極大可能改由非裔演員飾演。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，在 DC 漫畫的平行世界中已有兩位非裔超人，他們分別是來自地球 23 的 Calvin Ellis 和地球 2 的 Val-Zod。儘管官方尚未透露屆時是否「重啟」推出新版 Clark Kent，但外界多為猜測以 Calvin Ellis 或 Val-Zod 作為全新故事主角的可能性較大，如此一來便不會與 Henry Cavill 所飾演的超人有所衝突。此外，本次 Warner Bros. 和 DC 也特意找來知名劇作家 Ta-Nehisi Coates 擔任編劇，此前他曾為《黑豹》和《美國隊長》系列撰寫劇本並獲得優異成績。<br />\n<br />\n由於該電影仍處於早期開發階段，故關於將由誰來執導和具體走向尚未明朗，有關消息有待後續追蹤。"},{"pid":"9f5b816345f75f6859bec46ae2aa45771148594f","tid":2429691,"uid":170229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:24:11.000Z","msg":"過多幾年美國咸片男主角得番黑人，白人只能做cuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cda5aa0d75aeee4ef5a130f0da695def5761f7e","tid":2429691,"uid":165659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f5b816345f75f6859bec46ae2aa45771148594f","tid":2429691,"uid":170229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:24:11.000Z","msg":"過多幾年美國咸片男主角得番黑人，白人只能做cuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 